$ Inkscape menu: View -> Show/Hide

The available space for drawing might be made larger be hiding unneeded GUI elements.

The following elements can be shown or hidden:
table { ll
  Commands Bar ☰
  Snap Controls Bar ☰
  Tool Controls Bar ☰
  Toolbox ☰
  Rulers ☰ `Ctrl+R`
  Scrollbars ☰ `Ctrl+B`
  Palette ☰ `Shift+Alt+P`
  Statusbar ☰
table }
